## 🛩️ Aircraft Specifications
Currently featuring the **SR-71 Blackbird**:
- **Max Speed**: Mach 3.3 (1,100 m/s)
- **Service Ceiling**: 85,000 ft (25,908 m)
- **Engines**: Twin Pratt & Whitney J58
- **Mass**: 77,110 kg (170,000 lbs)

## 🏢 Airport Integration
The simulator loads real airport data from CSV files including:
- International airports (KJFK, KLAX, KORD, KATL)
- Runway specifications
- Geographic coordinates
- Elevation data

## 🔬 Physics Model
- **Aerodynamic Forces**: Lift, drag, thrust
- **Environmental**: Gravity, air density
- **Flight Dynamics**: Pitch, roll, yaw responses
- **Ground Interaction**: Basic collision detection

